<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV21">
<l>araṅkaṉēta raṅkanīrka laṅkavaṉṟu kuṉṟucūḻ</l>
<l>maraṅkaṭēya mānilaṅku luṅkamācu ṇañculāy</l>
<l>neruṅkanī kaṭaintapōtu niṉṟacūra reṉceytār</l>
<l>kuraṅkaiyā ḷukantaventai kūṟutēṟa vēṟitē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Raṅga! That day, You churned [the ocean],</l>
<l>Wound the snake tightly around [the Mandarā mountain]</l>
<l rend="indent">in such a way that the wavy sea was ruffled;</l>
<l rend="indent">in such a way that the trees surrounding the mountain wore away,</l>
<l rend="indent">in such a way that the great earth quaked.</l>
<l>What did the gods who stood by do [then]?</l>
<l>O Father who rejoiced in [and] ruled over the apes!</l>
<l>Tell [me] about this in a special [way] so that [I am] enlightened!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
